{"tid":1701120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈特有賣廣告大法：捐錢","createTime":"2019-11-09T01:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T01:01:42.000Z","uid":272805,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc9ec990efbd0827e487f8d42b255b0bf469958","tid":1701120,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"21世紀，仲洗乜用傳統方法宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如試吓一個雙贏方法<br />\n<br />\n做法好簡單<br />\n捐錢俾612、星火、或其他義務法律團隊<br />\n或者立場、蘋果、傳真社等是但一間傳媒<br />\n<br />\n之後貼出嚟，話俾大家知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n加入黃色經濟圈，大量黃絲等住罰你<br />\n幫到有需要的人士<br />\n錢唔會去到藍絲度<br />\n<br />\n完全係三贏嘅方案<br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔到<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得可行嘅唔該推一推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，還拖！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1cdc2d1e6b8fd02f84958bbe1cf14df67a773b87","tid":1701120,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲有Senator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=b8f17d7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（最新）Senator Scott 都出聲講議員被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a h